<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<!-- 앱 표시 이름 -->
	<key>CFBundleDisplayName</key>
	<string>Escapple</string>
	
	<!-- 앱 아이콘 설정 (visionOS용) -->
	<key>CFBundleIcons</key>
	<dict>
		<key>CFBundlePrimaryIcon</key>
		<string>AppIcon</string>
	</dict>
	
	<key>ARKitSupportedConfigurations</key>
	<array>
		<string>WorldTracking</string>
		<string>HandTracking</string>
	</array>
	<key>LSMinimumSystemVersion</key>
	<string>2.0</string>
	<key>NSAppTransportSecurity</key>
	<dict>
		<key>NSAllowsArbitraryLoads</key>
		<false/>
	</dict>
	<key>NSEnterpriseMCAMUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Escapple은 향상된 AR 경험과 정확한 환경 추적을 위해 엔터프라이즈 카메라 기능을 사용합니다. (Escapple uses enterprise camera features for enhanced AR experiences and accurate environment tracking.)</string>
	<key>NSHandsTrackingUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Escapple은 방탈출 게임에서 핸드 제스처를 통한 자연스러운 객체 조작을 위해 핸드 트래킹을 사용합니다. (Escapple uses hand tracking for natural object manipulation through hand gestures in the escape room game.)</string>
	<key>NSWorldSensingUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Escapple은 방탈출 환경에서 정확한 공간 추적과 가상 객체 상호작용을 제공하기 위해 월드 센싱을 사용합니다. (Escapple uses world sensing to provide accurate spatial tracking and interaction with virtual objects in the escape room environment.)</string>
	<key>UIApplicationSceneManifest</key>
	<dict>
		<key>UIApplicationPreferredDefaultSceneSessionRole</key>
		<string>UIWindowSceneSessionRoleApplication</string>
		<key>UIApplicationSupportsMultipleScenes</key>
		<true/>
		<key>UISceneConfigurations</key>
		<dict>
			<key>UISceneSessionRoleImmersiveSpaceApplication</key>
			<array>
				<dict>
					<key>UISceneInitialImmersionStyle</key>
					<string>UIImmersionStyleMixed</string>
				</dict>
			</array>
		</dict>
	</dict>
	<key>UIApplicationSupportsMultipleScenes</key>
	<true/>
	<key>UILaunchScreen</key>
	<dict>
		<key>UIImageName</key>
		<string></string>
	</dict>
</dict>
</plist>
